These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, watermelon
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, card-games
1. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food           | watermelon | lettuce |
| Hobby   | card-games     | writing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, may
2 different games are played: whist, scrabble
1. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Birthday         | may   | january      |
| Game   | whist | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, time-travel
1. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Game   | monopoly | mah-jongg    |
| Movie-Genre     | horror | time-travel |

 #################################

 
