.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
2 different pets are kept: rat, bird
2 different games are played: monopoly, billiard
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Pet   | bird | rat |
| Game     | billiard    | monopoly    |

