.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-8::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey
City: hamburg, miami
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | baseball    |
| City   | miami   | hamburg |

